data.eml:eml: On some Encyrtidae (Hymenoptera: Chalcidoidea) from Namdapha Tiger Reserve in Arunachal Pradesh, India

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Hayat, Mohammad, Kazmi, Sarfrazul Islam (2011): On some Encyrtidae (Hymenoptera: Chalcidoidea) from Namdapha Tiger Reserve in Arunachal Pradesh, India. Zootaxa 2830: 1-19, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.277296
